column2: select s.specobjid, gsl.h_alpha_flux as haflux, gsl.h_beta_flux as hbetaflux, gsl.oiii_#_flux as oiiiflux, smsp.metallicity as metallicity from galaxy p, specobj s, galspecline gsl, stellarmassstarformingport smsp where p.objid=s.bestobjid and s.specobjid=gsl.specobjid and gsl.specobjid=smsp.specobjid and s.subclass=starforming and s.z BETWEEN # AND # and s.snMedian># and gsl.oiii_#_flux># and gsl.h_beta_flux># and (gsl.oiii_#_flux/gsl.h_beta_flux) BETWEEN # and #
